'''Rojene Eborsisk''' was a [[Journalist/Legends|reporter]] for [[The Slasher Sun Times]] who [[Writing/Legends|wrote]] an article on [[Master Thespian]], and former [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]], [[Damien Tantrellius]]' play titled [[Jedi Men From Baronis]] for the Sun Times on [[Imperial Startime]] 45686.3467. Rojene made note that this play also featured Damien's daughter, [[Plum Tantrellius]], who played [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]]. Eborsisk also noted that his daughter was "not too hard to look at either".

